Mongo readme
cd C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\
created:

c:\data\db
c:\data\log

created a config file mongod.cfg

created the mongo service: sc.exe create MongoDB binPath= "\"C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\bin\mongod.exe\" --service --config=\"C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\mongod.cfg\"" DisplayName= "MongoDB" start= "auto"

started the mongo service: net start MongoDB

To stop:

net stop MongoDB

mongod --port 27017 --dbpath C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.6\data\db
